  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Official QQ group: 915133578</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Line up your Tetris! Choose your hero to acquire a block of buyers to match powerful combinations. Then brave Dracula's Castle and go into battle!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413140/extras/dcb7a5894dcdf8b526bc64d2814f1ed4.avif?t=1738738012\" width=700 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Monsters Under the Moonlight: Cube Brawl, you'll fight with Tetris. Your combat power depends on the choice of heroes, blocks, and most importantly in the placement of Tetris! The better you place, the stronger your fighting power will be!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413140/extras/d0fbf8a45de0f045eb3dfeb510cd3df7.poster.avif?t=1738738012\" width=384 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413140/extras/d0fbf8a45de0f045eb3dfeb510cd3df7.webm?t=1738738012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413140/extras/d0fbf8a45de0f045eb3dfeb510cd3df7.mp4?t=1738738012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are a total of 6 heroes to choose from, and different heroes have different talents. Your goal is to mix and match the blocks of your choice to maximize your hero's abilities! For example, attack speed flow, critical attack flow, meat shield flow, or blood line flow, etc.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413140/extras/f3443cfbc2f319db01c3450f34749aac.poster.avif?t=1738738012\" width=384 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413140/extras/f3443cfbc2f319db01c3450f34749aac.webm?t=1738738012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413140/extras/f3443cfbc2f319db01c3450f34749aac.mp4?t=1738738012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are fighting against a powerful enemy. Take a look at the enemy's talents and blocks and find a way to win.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413140/extras/329f0a91baa159bd9476338f870e4819.avif?t=1738738012\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413140/extras_big/329f0a91baa159bd9476338f870e4819.avif?t=1738738012 width=800 height=493 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Official QQ group: 915133578</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Line up your Tetris! Choose your hero to acquire a block of buyers to match powerful combinations. Then brave Dracula's Castle and go into battle!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413140/extras/dcb7a5894dcdf8b526bc64d2814f1ed4.avif?t=1738738012\" width=700 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Monsters Under the Moonlight: Cube Brawl, you'll fight with Tetris. Your combat power depends on the choice of heroes, blocks, and most importantly in the placement of Tetris! The better you place, the stronger your fighting power will be!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413140/extras/d0fbf8a45de0f045eb3dfeb510cd3df7.poster.avif?t=1738738012\" width=384 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413140/extras/d0fbf8a45de0f045eb3dfeb510cd3df7.webm?t=1738738012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413140/extras/d0fbf8a45de0f045eb3dfeb510cd3df7.mp4?t=1738738012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are a total of 6 heroes to choose from, and different heroes have different talents. Your goal is to mix and match the blocks of your choice to maximize your hero's abilities! For example, attack speed flow, critical attack flow, meat shield flow, or blood line flow, etc.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413140/extras/f3443cfbc2f319db01c3450f34749aac.poster.avif?t=1738738012\" width=384 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413140/extras/f3443cfbc2f319db01c3450f34749aac.webm?t=1738738012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413140/extras/f3443cfbc2f319db01c3450f34749aac.mp4?t=1738738012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are fighting against a powerful enemy. Take a look at the enemy's talents and blocks and find a way to win.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413140/extras/329f0a91baa159bd9476338f870e4819.avif?t=1738738012\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413140/extras_big/329f0a91baa159bd9476338f870e4819.avif?t=1738738012 width=800 height=493 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
